Collection of Linux Commands

Copy from Remote to Local using SCP
scp -r root@resly.me:/var/www/resly /Users/aligajani/Desktop

Copy from Local to Remote using SCP
scp -r /Users/aligajani/Desktop root@resly.me:/var/www/resly

Clone into a directory folder name of your choice
git clone https://github.com/aligajani/resly.me.git resly

Remove a folder and its constituent files
$ rm -rf